      <title>特鲁多表示联邦预算中将包含抵押贷款消息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/trudeau-says-news-on-mortgages-is-coming-in-federal-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多表示，他的政府将在即将到来的 4 月 16 日预算中宣布有关加拿大抵押贷款的消息，但没有提供更多细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/trudeau-says-news-on-mortgages-is-coming-in-federal-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 17:56:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
