      <title>吕特的北约领导权争夺面临东欧的要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/rutte-s-nato-leadership-bid-confronts-eastern-european-demands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马克·吕特领导北约的努力面临新的障碍，一些东欧国家向荷兰首相施压，要求增加该地区在军事联盟高层职位中的代表性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/rutte-s-nato-leadership-bid-confronts-eastern-european-demands</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 17:13:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合国秘书长对以色列利用人工智能寻找目标的报道感到“困扰”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/un-chief-troubled-by-reports-that-israel-used-ai-in-gaza-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯表示，他对以色列在加沙军事行动中使用人工智能的报道“深感不安”，称这种做法将平民置于危险之中，并模糊了责任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/un-chief-troubled-by-reports-that-israel-used-ai-in-gaza-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 17:10:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多推动 3D 打印预制房屋解决供应紧张问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/trudeau-pushes-3d-printed-prefabricated-homes-to-solve-supply-crunch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总理贾斯汀·特鲁多宣布了旨在使在加拿大建造新房变得更容易、更便宜的措施，重点是预制模块化住房。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/trudeau-pushes-3d-printed-prefabricated-homes-to-solve-supply-crunch</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 16:36:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰央行行长表示需要数字欧元来实现自治</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/dutch-central-banker-says-digital-euro-is-needed-for-autonomy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰央行行长克拉斯·诺特周五表示，欧洲需要数字欧元“以跟上社会的步伐，追求战略自主权，并在数字世界中保持获得公共资金的机会”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/dutch-central-banker-says-digital-euro-is-needed-for-autonomy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 16:28:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗要求美国靠边站，准备对以色列做出回应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/iran-tells-us-to-step-aside-as-it-readies-response-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗表示，在该国准备对以色列驻叙利亚领事馆涉嫌袭击事件做出回应之际，它要求美国“靠边站”，而其在中东的主要代理人真主党则警告这个犹太国家，它已做好战争准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/iran-tells-us-to-step-aside-as-it-readies-response-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 16:02:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
