      <title>特朗普 SPAC 证词定于同日刑事审判开始</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/trump-deposed-in-spac-lawsuit-the-day-of-start-of-criminal-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 定于 4 月 15 日在与其社交媒体初创公司有关的民事诉讼中接受质询，同日这位前总统的首次刑事审判也将开始。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/trump-deposed-in-spac-lawsuit-the-day-of-start-of-criminal-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 14:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
